{
  "message": "update(models): bump default model versions and add gpt-5.3-codex to snapshot\n\nsrc/app.rs \u2014 default_model_from_candidates():\n- Update minimax provider default from MiniMax-M2.1 to MiniMax-M2.5\n- Update minimax-cn provider default from MiniMax-M2.1 to MiniMax-M2.5\n- Update opencode provider default from claude-opus-4-5 to claude-opus-4-6\n\nThese changes track the latest flagship releases from MiniMax (M2.5)\nand Anthropic (Opus 4.6), ensuring that when pi_agent selects a\ndefault model for these providers it uses the most capable current\nversion.\n\ndocs/provider-upstream-model-ids-snapshot.json:\n- Add \"gpt-5.3-codex\" to the sorted list of known upstream model IDs\n\nThis keeps the reference snapshot in sync with newly available models\nso that provider-mapping validation and tests remain accurate.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
